      "acceptanceCriteria": "FEA solver (Ansys Mechanical 2022 R1) holds a documented software quality plan including version control, regression testing, and traceable release notes. Level 2 is required because model risk is moderate and the solver is a commercial validated code.",
      "rationale": "Ansys Mechanical 2022 R1 is used under a documented SQA plan. Version control and regression test records are on file. Achieved level matches required level."
