    "rationale": "All 13 V&V 40 credibility factors assessed. Twelve of thirteen factors meet or exceed their required levels. One factor (Test conditions) achieves Level 2 against a required Level 3 due to the single-condition ASTM F1717 protocol; this shortfall is accepted because the COU is narrowly scoped to the F1717 static compression-bending configuration and the quantitative acceptance criteria for output comparison are fully satisfied. Overall credibility is judged sufficient for a Medium assurance level regulatory submission.",
